snippet.title: Underhell September 1 2023 Livestream
snippet.description:
To celebrate the 10th anniversary of the release of Underhell Chapter 1, we did a livestream on September 1st, 2023.

It took me a while to upload this because I originally wanted to edit it and remove some of the crashes or lul moments for viewing ease. A few people suggested I upload the raw recording and I spent too much time overthinking it and putting it off.

Last few months have been challenging, just lost my job at NWI on Monday December 4th, 2023. Not sure what I'm doing next, we shall see!

Enjoy the livestream, it was a wonderful time. I am humbled by all the people who are still keeping this alive. Thank you so much, I love you all.

I'll see you when I see you. Not too early, not too late.
